Hokkaido Governor Approves Tomari Commercial Restart, Kyodo Says

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-08-17T04:56:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/hokkaido-governor-approves-tomari-commercial-restart-kyodo-says.html
Japan ’s Hokkaido prefecture approved
the commercial restart of Hokkaido Electric Power Co.’s Tomari
No. 3 nuclear reactor,  Kyodo News  reported, citing governor
Harumi Takahashi.  The restart is the first return to commercial operations
for a nuclear reactor since the disaster at Fukushima Dai-Ichi,
Kyodo said. The reactor has been producing power as part of test
operations since March.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
